<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Billet - {{ evenement.titre }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
        }
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #0ea5e9; /* accent-blue */
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .row {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .column {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .left-column {
            width: 65%;
        }
        .right-column {
            width: 30%;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .qr-code {
            max-width: 150px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            background: #10b981;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>TICKET D'ENTRÉE</h1>
            <p>Présentez ce billet (imprimé ou sur smartphone) le jour de l'événement.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="column left-column">
                    <div class="badge">{{ evenement.typeEvenement }}</div>
                    
                    <div class="info-label">Événement</div>
                    <div class="info-value" style="font-size: 22px; color: #0284c7;">{{ evenement.titre }}</div>
                    
                    <div class="info-label">Participant</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{ utilisateur.prenom }} {{ utilisateur.nom }} ({{ utilisateur.email }})</div>
                    
                    <div class="info-label">Date et Heure</div>
                    <div class="info-value">Le {{ evenement.dateDebut|date('d/m/Y') }} à {{ evenement.dateDebut|date('H:i') }}</div>
                    
                    <div class="info-label">Lieu</div>
                    <div class="info-value">{{ evenement.lieu }}</div>
                    
                    <div class="info-label">Référence du Billet</div>
                    <div class="info-value" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; color: #475569;">{{ participation.jeton }}</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="column right-column">
                    <div class="info-label">QR CODE UNIQUE</div>
                    <img src="{{ qrCode }}" alt="QR Code SCAN" class="qr-code">
                    <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center; margin-top: 8px;">Réservé à l'administration</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>MatchNTeam — Reconnectez vos collaborateurs aux moments importants.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 5px; opacity: 0.7;">Généré le {{ 'now'|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
